Lucy has labeled the current Head of House, Erica as insincere. Lucy said Erica pretends to be a good girl one minute and the next minutes she’s something else. Erica and Lucy have had several fallouts in the House. However, on Friday, during her diary session, Lucy said she can’t be friends with someone with Erica’s attitude. She said it is better to stick to one character than being double-faced in different situations. She said: “Erica would act bitchy one minute and the next minute she comes to you seeking peace and I’m like you can’t be that way. “Choose one side of you and stop being two-faced. That was why I ignored her